  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Idle Planets</strong> is an incremental game where you mine planets, automate production, and expand your reach across the cosmos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your wealth, unlock new worlds, and become the richest miner in the galaxy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🪐 <strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Planets to unlock and upgrade</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full automation system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >700+ powerful upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Permanent ascension bonuses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random events to boost production</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768260/extras/40b4a152f09ac5eb0a9f91b06fcdd296.poster.avif?t=1760623768\" width=600 height=227 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768260/extras/40b4a152f09ac5eb0a9f91b06fcdd296.webm?t=1760623768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌌 Brand New Second Galaxy</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 new planets to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New asteroid types: Spam Rock, Discount Rock & more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alien helpers with unique boosts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanded ascension and automation systems</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768260/extras/5d9ab6c7994726a2e7b08a3bbea9ee40.poster.avif?t=1760623768\" width=645 height=363 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768260/extras/5d9ab6c7994726a2e7b08a3bbea9ee40.webm?t=1760623768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn, expand, and climb the <strong>five leaderboards</strong> to prove who’s the richest miner in the universe.</p>",
